      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "天气会在晴、阴、雨之间来回切换。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-stationary",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-stationary/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.64,
      "size": 26208,
      "text": "如果观察足够多天，晴天大约占多少比例？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-stationary",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-stationary/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.5,
      "size": 24048,
      "text": "这个长期占比，正是马氏链的稳态分布。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-stationary",
      "section_id": "matrix",
      "line_id": "mat-1",
      "filename": "matrix-mat-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-stationary/xiaoxiao/matrix-mat-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "把每天转到下一天的概率排成一张表，就是转移矩阵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-stationary",
      "section_id": "matrix",
      "line_id": "mat-2",
      "filename": "matrix-mat-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-stationary/xiaoxiao/matrix-mat-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "它的每一行之和都是一，因为明天总要落到某个状态。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-stationary",
      "section_id": "matrix",
      "line_id": "mat-3",
      "filename": "matrix-mat-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-stationary/xiaoxiao/matrix-mat-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "比如今天晴，明天有七成继续晴，两成转阴，一成下雨。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-stationary",
      "section_id": "iterate",
      "line_id": "iter-1",
      "filename": "iterate-iter-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-stationary/xiaoxiao/iterate-iter-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "把今天的分布左乘转移矩阵，就得到明天的分布。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-stationary",
      "section_id": "iterate",
      "line_id": "iter-2",
      "filename": "iterate-iter-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-stationary/xiaoxiao/iterate-iter-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.47,
      "size": 23472,
      "text": "反复相乘，分布就一天天向前演化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-stationary",
      "section_id": "iterate",
      "line_id": "iter-3",
      "filename": "iterate-iter-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-stationary/xiaoxiao/iterate-iter-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "看柱状图，各状态的比例在逐步调整。"
